description:
MindCrack FTB is a modded Minecraft server Guude has setup for the MindCrackers. It is a private (whitelisted) server. We are currently not accepting applications.

Today we join forces with the beloved BdoubleO to solve the mystery of what happened to our shops and of the new Pawn Shop that has appeared in town.
